00:14:21,240 --> 00:14:24,960
perspective on poverty and on humanity.
对贫困和人性的看法。

329
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:27,700
And you think about, well, you know, I could be this person.
你会想，嗯，你知道，我可能也会变成这个人。

330
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:30,880
He was a banker two years ago and now he doesn't have a house.
他两年前还是个银行家，现在却无家可归。

331
00:14:30,880 --> 00:14:33,920
And so I think it has a positive effect on everybody involved.
所以我认为这对所有参与者都有积极的影响。

332
00:14:33,920 --> 00:14:34,920
Yeah, for sure.
是的，当然。

333
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:37,000
No, I think it's a very rewarding experience.
不，我认为这是一次非常有意义的经历。

334
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:42,160
And I think EnglishPod definitely supports that you should volunteer, you should make
而且我认为EnglishPod绝对支持你应该做志愿者，你应该

335
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,160
a difference.
做出改变。

336
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:45,600
And I think we can all help each other, right?
而且我认为我们都可以互相帮助，对吧？

337
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,600
That's right.
没错。

338
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:48,000
Have you ever volunteered?
你做过志愿者吗？

339
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,680
What kind of volunteer work have you done?
你做过哪种志愿工作？

340
00:14:49,680 --> 00:14:51,840
Has it been environmental or social?
是环保方面的还是社会方面的？

341
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:53,760
Let us know on our website, EnglishPod.com.
请在我们的网站EnglishPod.com上告诉我们。

342
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:54,760
We hope to see you there.
我们希望能在那里见到你。

343
00:14:54,760 --> 00:14:55,760
All right.
好了。

344
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:56,760
Bye, everyone.
大家再见。

345
00:14:56,760 --> 00:15:16,760
Thank you.
谢谢。
